title: Shenwu Tianzun – Manhuaus
summary: READ [Shenwu Tianzun] English At [MANHUAUS.COM] I was once the Supreme God of Physique, standing tall above others. However, I was betrayed by those whom I thought of as my most trustworthy friends. They had schemed against me in an attempt to kill me, which was almost successful. Fortunately, a fraction of my soul had managed to escape into the body of a seriously injured child giving me another chance at life, and revenge.
